name: Serie Tribute: 09 - Jack Frost
description:
This new series has a collectible card format. It will make a tribute tour about superheroes and villains. A new creative venture of Roboto Inc. for its great collectors. Prototypes designed by Norma Xelda Jara. Let's have fun! 

Jack Frost is a fictional superhero appearing in American comic books published by Marvel Comics.
First appeared in 1941 in U.S.A. Comics.
Jack Frost has the ability to generate sub-zero temperatures. Combined with ambient water vapor, he can create snow, sleet and ice for various effects, such as propelling snow flurries at the wind speed of hurricanes or turning ice into various simple constructions such as spheres, bridges or walls. He also has superhuman strength and durability. Jack Frost has a bluish-white skin that glows from the frost glaze that covers it. His skin temperature is 32 ° F (0 ° C).
